1. *Ljudski* odnosi su postali hladni i distancirani. (Human relations have become cold and distant.)

2. On se pona≈°a razumno i *ljudski*. (He behaves reasonably and humanely.)

3. Nije u skladu sa *ljudskim* vrednostima. (It is not in accordance with human values.)

4. On je postigao veliki *ljudski* uspeh. (He achieved a great human success.)

5. Nije u skladu sa *ljudskim* interesima. (It is not in accordance with human interests.)

6. Oni su bili veoma *ljudski*. (They were very humane.)